Ex-BBNaija 2019 housemate Thelma has recalled how a relative maltreated and attempted to infect her with HIV while she was living with her family as a child. The relative and her husband, she alleged, lashed her with horsewhip. The movie star also noted her relative spat into her mouth on one of those days she was being flogged with the intent of infecting her with HIV/AIDS. She recalled God used a woman who travelled down to the village to inform her mother of the maltreatment she was being subjected to. - Advertisement - Thelma wrote: “Years ago when I was a kid staying with a relative of mine, she was married and was living with her husband but no child.   Mr Macaroni: I don’t hate any government official but…     Bella Shmurda replies LASU over plea to complete degree…     Ex-Miss USA Cheslie Kryst dies after jumping from 29th floor   “This woman would flog me koboko in the night for no reason and the husband would wake me up with koboko in the morning telling me it’s his turn. “2 things I can’t forget: How she flogged me one day and spat into my mouth. How God used a woman from my place to save me by traveling home to tell my mum to come to carry me before I die. “Long story short. A few weeks after I left, the woman died, and afterward, the man died too. “It was said that they were both living with HIV and AIDS and that woman wanted me to contract it by spitting into my mount but God said NO! “I don’t know where they are now but I forgive them.”